{"tid":920130,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"劉德華首新歌真係好難頂","createTime":"2018-11-28T15:07:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T16:43:13.000Z","uid":176553,"like":26,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"dcd71340dfa78631f2c5050da1d9db64b5a47d8e","tid":920130,"uid":176553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T15:07:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xmjk3r2rIsA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fxmjk3r2rIsA&d=48PVRAkZfDVe9iXCZP5KMdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=8ebbf404\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xmjk3r2rIsA</a><br />\n<br />\n咪怪世界缺乏愛<br />\n其實世界到處也是愛<br />\n要開心 放開悲哀<br />\n<br />\n你有勇氣接受我<br />\n然後你要試試抱緊我<br />\n親親我 時常親我<br />\n<br />\n你啱啱跟我剛剛<br />\n轉眼熱烈地啊盛放<br />\n要熱烈地 為愛闖禍<br />\n<br />\n世界變了繼續愛<br />\n無論個個笑我繼續愛<br />\n將一對 成為一個<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMy Love (Whoa-oh-oh)<br />\n有花堪折直須折 Baby<br />\nWhoa Whoa<br />\nMy Love (Whoa-oh-oh)<br />\n莫待無花空折枝<br />\n望小姐了解當中意思"},{"pid":"8e8f679200a522ec786a7a9b2cb95776f3adf3a3","tid":920130,"uid":53855,"like":6,"dislike":7,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T15:34:17.000Z","msg":"幾正，做演唱會主題曲氣氛一流"},{"pid":"c4e1cb861351fe9f0e16ec0165bec9b56bbd5e7c","tid":920130,"uid":53855,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T15:35:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kS_ktwyt4y4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkS_ktwyt4y4&d=48PVRAkZfDVe9iXCZP5KMdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=0d7c2c58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kS_ktwyt4y4</a>"},{"pid":"e78dddb45cefa4c0f39cccb84cf6fe09b3f05c29","tid":920130,"uid":213441,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T15:36:43.000Z","msg":"無啦啦整句古詩做乜鳩"},{"pid":"7d86a9666aed27c7569bc84a8be35828dde56b57","tid":920130,"uid":61205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T15:38:18.000Z","msg":"24k Magic？"},{"pid":"e5fcdd67011a79e4f7690e4c72ea8a4e5344dfde","tid":920130,"uid":37431,"like":23